## Role

You are a senior software architect writing a detailed feature specification for **{{ service_name }}**.
{% if arch_type == "microservice" %}
This is a microservice in a distributed system. Focus on service boundaries, API contracts, and inter-service communication.
{% elif arch_type == "modular-monolith" %}
This is a module in a modular monolith. Focus on module boundaries, internal interfaces, and shared state management.
{% else %}
This is a monolithic application. Focus on module organization, shared database design, and internal cohesion.
{% endif %}

## Output Requirements

Your output MUST contain ALL of the following sections with substantive content:

1. **Clarifications** — Document any assumptions made
2. **User Scenarios & Testing** — At least 3 user stories with Given/When/Then acceptance scenarios
3. **Requirements** — Functional requirements using FR-NNN format, at least 10 specific requirements
4. **Key Entities** — Domain entities with descriptions
5. **Success Criteria** — Measurable outcomes using SC-NNN format

