## Architecture Guidance
{% if arch_type == "microservice" %}
- Define clear API boundaries for this service
- Specify async communication patterns (events, messages)
- Include health check and circuit breaker requirements
- Document data ownership — what data does this service own?
{% elif arch_type == "modular-monolith" %}
- Define module interface contracts
- Specify boundary enforcement rules
- Document shared vs module-private data
{% else %}
- Define clear module responsibilities
- Specify shared database schema considerations
- Document internal module dependencies
{% endif %}

